OL,3,CThe self-made tycoon now dubbed a
OL,4,C'monster': Who was Mohamed Al Fayed?
OL,6,FMultiple ex-employees of the luxury
OL,7,Fdepartment store Harrods have accused
OL,8,Fthe store's former owner - the late
OL,9,FMohamed Al Fayed - of sexual abuse.
OL,11,FA lawyer representing multiple women
OL,12,Fhas branded Al Fayed a "monster", and
OL,13,Fsaid the allegations are among the
OL,14,Fworst he has dealt with.
OL,16,FThe Egypt-born tycoon, who died in
OL,17,FSeptember 2023 aged 94, was a
OL,18,Fcontroversial and often abrasive
OL,19,Fbusinessman who never shied away from
OL,20,Fa fight - even taking on the royal
OL,21,Ffamily.
