OL,3,CThe self-made tycoon now dubbed a
OL,4,C'monster': Who was Mohamed Al Fayed?
OL,6,FITV News explains how he became a
OL,7,Fbusiness tycoon - and the controversy
OL,8,Fbehind his life and work.
OL,10,FFrom the streets of Alexandria to a
OL,11,Fself-made billionaire
OL,13,FAl Fayed's created a billion-pound
OL,14,Fbusiness empire in his adopted UK,
OL,15,Fincluding upmarket department store
OL,16,FHarrods, which led to the Egyptian
OL,17,Fbeing dubbed the "Phoney Pharaoh".
