OL,4,C'monster': Who was Mohamed Al Fayed?
OL,6,FFulham were languishing in Division
OL,7,FTwo when he took over in 1997 after Al
OL,8,FFayed spent money on players and high-
OL,9,Fprofile managers, including Kevin
OL,10,FKeegan and Roy Hodgson, the club rose
OL,11,Fto the top-half of the Premier League
OL,12,Fin the early Noughties, peaking in
OL,13,Fqualification for the Europa League.
OL,15,FOff the pitch, fans were treated to
OL,16,Fsome bizarre spectacles, including a
OL,17,F1999 visit from Al Fayed's friend
OL,18,FMichael Jackson.
