OL,6,FThe Harrods boss and the club faced
OL,7,Fsome ridicule when, in 2011, two years
OL,8,Fafter Jackson's death, a statue of the
OL,9,FKing Of Pop was erected at its Craven
OL,10,FCottage ground.
OL,12,FWhen Al Fayed sold the club in 2013 it
OL,13,Fwas taken down, and Fulham were later
OL,14,Frelegated.
