OL,3,CThe self-made tycoon now dubbed a
OL,4,C'monster': Who was Mohamed Al Fayed?
OL,6,FAl Fayed's most public attack was on
OL,7,Fthe House of Windsor and the
OL,8,FEstablishment over the death of his
OL,9,Fson and heir Dodi ` alongside Diana,
OL,10,FPrincess of Wales, in a car crash in
OL,11,FParis in 1997.
OL,13,FThe tycoon spent a decade after their
OL,14,Fdeaths repeatedly claiming they were
OL,15,Fmurdered in a plot by the security
OL,16,Fservices and the Duke of Edinburgh.
OL,18,FBut he was forced to reluctantly
OL,19,Fconcede defeat after a high-profile
OL,20,Fsix-month inquest in 2007 and 2008.
