OL,3,CThe self-made tycoon now dubbed a
OL,4,C'monster': Who was Mohamed Al Fayed?
OL,6,FThe jury returned unlawful killing
OL,7,Fverdicts on both Diana and Dodi, but
OL,8,Fpinned the blame on the drink-driving
OL,9,Fof their chauffeur Henri Paul, who
OL,10,Falso died in the crash.
OL,12,FPaul was employed by the Paris Ritz,
OL,13,Fwhere Diana and Dodi had had dinner on
OL,14,FAugust 31, a hotel owned by Mr Al
OL,15,FFayed.
