OL,6,FAt the end of the inquest, coroner
OL,7,FLord Justice Scott Baker openly voiced
OL,8,Fsuggestions of "closing ranks" at the
OL,9,Fhotel over the question of whether
OL,10,Fthey knew Paul was drinking on the
OL,11,Fnight of the incident.
OL,13,FThe jury had heard allegations,
OL,14,Fstrenuously denied, that key witnesses
OL,15,Fwere pressurised into backing Al
OL,16,FFayed's theories and there was a
OL,17,F"conspiracy to pervert the truth"
OL,18,Fwithin the Fayed organisation.
